, "text_ar": "غُسْل"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "for his visit to every one of them; and being asked wherefore he did so, he answered,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_in~ahu A^a*okaru", "text_ar": "اـِنَّهُ اَذْكَرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It is more,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "most, sharp"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "effective"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHad~u", "text_ar": "اَحَدُّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, TA, from a trad.) And it was said to Ibn-Ez-Zubeyr, when he was prostrated,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waA@ll~`hi maA waladati Aln~isaA='u A^a*okara minoka", "text_ar": "وَا@للّٰهِ مَا وَلَدَتِ النِّسَا=ءُ اَذْكَرَ مِنْكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "By God, women have not brought forth one more acute and ardent and vigorous and effective in affairs than thou."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA from a trad.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}